{"tid":2352160,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"呢隊巴塞不如執左佢啦","createTime":"2021-01-03T21:58:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T10:35:09.000Z","uid":30306,"like":23,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6cf42800f321b548eb9ed9ec85e1e905c8f694cc","tid":2352160,"uid":30306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T21:58:06.000Z","msg":"Now兩個旁述成場係咁講雖然0:1<br />\n但係好好睇 什麼精神面貌係今季最好<br />\n<br />\n仆你個街 成場控球7成幾<br />\n射門無幾球中龍 成撚日比兩個攻勢終結者斷波<br />\n一個就柏迪 一個就丹比利<br />\n係到講丹比利後生 條友黎左巴塞幾耐？<br />\nfirst touch成塊屎咁 傷仲多過踢<br />\n柏迪下下醫院波 ok地滑由佢<br />\n正前鋒得一球起腳 入波個下拉開人仲做左乜<br />\n得一個迪莊係想贏 入完一粒係到妹下妹下<br />\n<br />\n對面榜尾贏得1場<br />\n你贏1球羞唔羞家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWho needs so9?<br />\n實有人話馬體會都和啦<br />\n人地打少幾場排榜首 你排幾阿<br />\n呢隊巴執撚左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b6f9184e65e714c4159fc695ca3cd0c0fa7e8d5","tid":2352160,"uid":30306,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T21:59:51.000Z","msg":"入完1粒 <span class=\"red\">半隊</span>係到妹下妹下"},{"pid":"5bf0e92408af49aad69bfb6acc5816f81262fd38","tid":2352160,"uid":65598,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T22:02:51.000Z","msg":"睇住個盤黎踢姐 同勁唔勁無關"},{"pid":"7643bc83793572bf5e44e126ce528c502905e0fb","tid":2352160,"uid":78243,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T22:04:09.000Z","msg":"睇得出買左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d0d9c5140d85a30eea7e1da7a316237f78d0a4","tid":2352160,"uid":209999,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5bf0e92408af49aad69bfb6acc5816f81262fd38","tid":2352160,"uid":65598,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T22:02:51.000Z","msg":"睇住個盤黎踢姐 同勁唔勁無關"},"citedBy":1,"replyTi